ation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/715cc0ad8bde7c0fd87bc54b8fbf4cf19ddb9ef1" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
